org.osate.aadl2.instance

Interface InstancePackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    InstancePackage

    public static interface InstancePackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
